These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  manager, project-manager, musician, teacher, journalist, nurse, accountant
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, colombian, russian, pakistani, german, indonesian, spanish
 1. the teacher is on the left of the pakistani##1
 2. the german is the teacher##1
 3. the accountant is on the right of the nurse##1
 4. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
 5. the musician is in the middle##1
 6. the indian is on the far left##1
 7. the journalist is the indian##1
 8. the manager is on the right of the indonesian##1
 9. the russian is on the left of the colombian##1
10. the pakistani is on the left of the musician##1
11. the accountant is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | journalist | teacher | project-manager | musician | manager | nurse | accountant |
| Nationality   | indian    | german   | pakistani      | indonesian | russian    | colombian    | spanish         |

