.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: potato, pomegranate, kiwi, apricot, grapefruit, artichoke, pumpkin
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, house, dubstep, disco, r&b, salsa, folk
 1. the fan of r&b is the person eating apricot##1
 2. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person eating apricot is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 6. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 7. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 9. the fan of folk is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating apricot is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | potato | pomegranate | grapefruit | apricot | artichoke | pumpkin | kiwi |
| Music-Genre   | house      | dubstep   | disco   | r&b      | trance       | folk       | salsa     |

