.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, grapes, potato, peas, eggplant, apple, asparagus
The people have 7 different jobs:  fisherman, architect, electrician, firefighter, engineer, social-worker, software-developer
 1. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the software-developer##1
 3. the architect is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 4. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 5. the fisherman is the person eating eggplant##1
 6. the electrician is on the right of the architect##1
 7. the architect is on the left of the electrician##1
 8. the architect is on the right of the firefighter##1
 9. the person eating apple is the firefighter##1
10. the person eating potato is on the right of the fisherman##1
11. the firefighter is in the middle##1
12. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | grapes | eggplant     | potato  | apple       | broccoli       | asparagus  | peas   |
| Job    | social-worker  | fisherman | software-developer | firefighter | architect | electrician | engineer |

