.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: soul, punk, techno, trance, pop, salsa, funk
There are 7 different nationalities: american, russian, canadian, spanish, chinese, mexican, malaysian
 1. the fan of pop is the russian##1
 2. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 3. the mexican is on the right of the canadian##1
 4. the american is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 5. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 6. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 7. the canadian is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the fan of techno is on the right of the mexican##1
 9. the fan of techno is the chinese##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the fan of punk##1
11. the malaysian is the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | funk     | trance     | techno      | punk | pop      | soul     |
| Nationality   | spanish | canadian | mexican | chinese | malaysian | russian | american |

