.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: collecting, skydiving, baking, traveling, lizarding, hiking, filmmaking
7 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, cat, pony, rat, hamster, chinchilla
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is lizarding##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is lizarding is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's hobby is lizarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | skydiving | baking | hiking     | traveling | filmmaking | lizarding | collecting |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | cat    | rat | hamster     | ferret         | pony     | lizard        |

