.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, water, hot-chocolate, fanta, tea, lemonade, mirinda
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, subway, train, taxi, snowmobile, car, scooter
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person drinking cola is the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | lemonade   | cola | fanta | mirinda  | tea | water |
| Transport   | taxi   | snowmobile | airplane | car     | subway | scooter | train   |

