.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, epic, fantasy, musical, mystery, spy, zombie
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, ship, taxi, bus, train, tram, airplane
 1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the car is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | zombie | musical | mystery | spy     | epic | fantasy |
| Transport     | tram | bus      | airplane | taxi    | train | ship   | car  |

