 6. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating lime##1
 7. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating orange##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
