 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1

